name: Farewell Show DVD
description:
The official DVD of the farewell Pegasus Bridge show

Manchester - Sept 17th 2011

The full show, plus extra footage with fans as well as the bands official promo videos for the singles Ribena, Like Dogs and Yoko

Extra - There will be a golden ticket in one of the DVDs, with the lucky winner receiving Callum's keyboard that he smashed at end of the show!
